com.attribyte.json

Class JSONToJsoup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.attribyte.json.JSONToJsoup

  • public class JSONToJsoup
extends Object
    Parses JSON to a tree of jsoup nodes.

    Among other uses, the parsed tree may be queried using jsoup's Selector system.

    Author:
    Matt Hamer, Attribyte, LLC
